Posted: Thu May 03, 2012 1:27 pm
If you are ever curious what is accredited, always check with the accreditation...http://main.abet.org/aps/AccreditedProg ... tionID=145But on topic, if you are asking if an "Engineering Science" degree is the same as an EE or ME... most employers will tell you it isn't. That doesn't mean you won't know as much, or be able to do as much work -- it's just that any potential employer may be looking for an EE or ME, and not see any on your resume.Just some food for thought.
